{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/RTS_Quote.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>S A M U D R A</strong> is a hand-illustrated, 2D puzzle game that follows a child's adventure across a polluted sea. Players encounter underwater creatures to uncover truths about \u201csurface-dweller\u201d actions causing the polluted deep-sea world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/Steam_AboutGame_Prologue.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>E X P E R I E N C E</strong> - a uniquely designed story without dialogue, Samudra is accessible across lingual and auditory borders.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/Steam_AboutGame_CoralGrave.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>E X P L O R E</strong> - a polluted underwater world filled with surreal discoveries &amp; challenges, all beautifully hand-illustrated. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/Steam_AboutGame_OilRig.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>E N C O U N T E R</strong> - Deep Sea dwellers, creatures, characters, and tons, tons, tons of pollution.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/Steam_AboutGame_StoneCave.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>E M O T I O N A L</strong> - journey that depicts being at rock-bottom, and the long arduous trip back to reach the surface. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116260/extras/Steam_AboutGame_Sunken_City.png?t=1728728391\" /><br><br><strong>E N V I R O N M E N T A L</strong> - activism is synonymous with the project, the profits from this project are channeled towards year-round collaborations with the Ind